{"lemma":"دُثُرِ","slug":"دُثُرِ","root":"د.ث.ر","root_slug":"د-ث-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/د-ث-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n12095","n12099","n12100","n12101"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AF%D9%8F%D8%AB%D9%8F%D8%B1%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"copious water, abundant supply of water"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/daθr/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n12095","headword_ar":"دَثَرَ","root":"dvr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, K, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duvuwrN","text_ar":"دُثُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, K, &c.,) said of a trace, or mark, of a house; or of what remains, cleaving to the ground, marking the place of a house; (S, Msb, K, TA;) or of a place of abode, (T, A,) &c.; (T;) or of a thing; (M;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became covered with sand and dust blown over it by the wind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"this is the primary signification: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it became effaced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obliterated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, A, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by the blowing of the winds over it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tdAvr","text_ar":"تداثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Andvr","text_ar":"اندثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it became old;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Andvr","text_ar":"اندثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tdAvr","text_ar":"تداثر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) By one of the poets it is metaphorically said of a man's reputation, meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became worn out of regard"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"notice; became effaced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obliterated."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) ―         -b2-  And, said of a man, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became overcome by old age and emaciation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA.) ―         -b3-  Also, said of a garment, (T, K,) inf. n. as above, (T,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became dirty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K.) ―         -b4-  And, said of a sword, (T, A, K,) inf. n. as above, (A,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became sullied from remaining long unfurbished;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it became rusty."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K.) Hence the trad. of El-Hasan,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAdivuwA h`*ihi Alquluwba bi*ikori","text_ar":"حَادِثُوا هٰذِهِ القُلُوبَ بِذِكْرِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@ll~`hu faA_in~ahaA sariyEapu Ald~uvuwri","text_ar":"ا@للّٰهُ فَاـِنَّهَا سَرِيعَةُ الدُّثُورِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[explained in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hdv","text_ar":"حدث"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Sh, T, A, TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duvuwrN","text_ar":"دُثُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"attributed to the heart is (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having the remembrance of God effaced from it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and attributed to the mind, (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"being quick to forget."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, T, K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"davara Al$~ajaru","text_ar":"دَثَرَ الشَّجَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n. as above; (TA; [in which, by a strange mistake,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alrjl","text_ar":"الرجل"},{"kind":"text","text":"is put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$jr","text_ar":"الشجر"},{"kind":"text","text":";]) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dv~r","text_ar":"دثّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (so in the M, accord. to the TT;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The trees put forth their leaves"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and their branches."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["M","Msb","T","A","TA","S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n12099","headword_ar":"دَثْرٌ","root":"dvr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Much property"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wealth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"many camels"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"many,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of any thing or things: (M:) [the sing. and dual and pl. are alike; as in the case of its syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diborN","text_ar":"دِبْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daborN","text_ar":"دَبْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] you say, [using it as an epithet,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAlN daborN","text_ar":"مَالٌ دَبْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAlaAni davorN","text_ar":"مَالَانِ دَثْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^amowaAli davorN","text_ar":"اَمْوَالِ دَثْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) [but sometimes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duvuwrN","text_ar":"دُثُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used as its pl.; for] you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholu davorK","text_ar":"اَهْلُ دَثْرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aholu duvuwrK","text_ar":"اَهْلُ دُثُورٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (A 'Obeyd, T:) you also say ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAlN divorN","text_ar":"مَالٌ دِثْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T:) and the expression ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EasokarN davarN","text_ar":"عَسْكَرٌ دَثَرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a numerous army,"},{"kind":"text","text":"occurs thus written: (S:) an instance is found in a verse of Imra-el-Keys, where it is thus for the sake of the metre. (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Abundance of herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abundant herbage, and the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAvirN","text_ar":"دَاثِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","K"]},{"entry_id":"n12100","headword_ar":"دِثْرٌ","root":"dvr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"davorN","text_ar":"دَثْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"divorN maAlK","text_ar":"دِثْرٌ مَالٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A good manager of property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of camels"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n12101","headword_ar":"دَثَرٌ","root":"dvr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dirt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"davorN","text_ar":"دَثْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}